Template for playing cards, will automatically color the suits with the standard red/black. To see a [[w:4-color deck|4-color deck]], copy the following into your [[Special:MyPage/skin.css|user style sheet]]:

 /* Standard four-color deck */
 .diamonds { color: blue !important }
 .clubs { color: green !important }

=== Usage ===
{{tlx|cards|Ac|Kd|Ts|2h}} and {{tlx|cards|A♣|K♦|10♠|2♥}} will produce the same output:

:{{tlx|cards|Ac|Kd|Ts|2h}} &rarr; {{cards|Ac|Kd|Ts|2h}}
:{{tlx|cards|A♣|K♦|10♠|2♥}} &rarr; {{cards|A♣|K♦|10♠|2♥}}

Stand-alone suit symbols: {{tlx|cards|c|d|s|h}} gives {{cards|c|d|s|h}}.

