{{question-answer|question=moon.|answer=An astronomical object that orbits around a planet.}}
{{question-answer|question=Solar System.|answer=The Sun with the (dwarf) planets and their moons.}}

''8 points can be earned with this task. A wrong or bad description gives 0 points, a reasonable description gives 1 point, a good description gives 2 points.''

