*User X wants to send email to Y. They go to <tt>example.com/mail.php</tt> and notice some words. The form says that he has had over 100 spam emails sent via the form.
*Spammer S edits a page on wiki W. The wiki had been spammed before. They notice that the page is not saved with their spamming software.
